&quot;Atkins Jefferson McLemore (March 13, 1857 - March 4, 1929) was an American newspaper publisher, State Representative and United States Representative from Texas.&quot;
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._Jeff_McLemore" rel="nofollow">en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._Jeff_McLemore</a>

Several newspapers reported that he wrote his name &quot;Jeff: McLemore&quot;, see e.g. <a href="http://chroniclingamerica.loc.gov/lccn/sn84024827/1916-02-25/ed-1/seq-1/" rel="nofollow">Bisbee daily review., February 25, 1916, Image 1</a>, with photo.
